{"tid":2023911,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"抗戰一周年","createTime":"2020-05-19T09:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T10:41:57.000Z","uid":80564,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8c49b3e211bfbe4d61e44d960a47f109c028bf6a","tid":2023911,"uid":80564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:56:20.000Z","msg":"抗戰一周年<br />\n濟作曲：黃家駒<br />\n編曲：Beyond<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n＊喔　你我霎眼抗戰一周年   香港怎變　我答應你那五點　不會變<br />\n<br />\n當六一二空臂我們就上街　沒什麼聲勢浩大<br />\n但被不安養大　不足養大　哪裡怕表態<br />\n當中一起經過了時代瓦解　中大執位再到理大<br />\n路上風急雨大　一起嚇大　聽慣了警戒<br />\n<br />\n應該珍惜的　即使犧牲了　激起的火花　仍然照耀<br />\n<br />\nRepeat＊<br />\n<br />\n幾響槍火敲破了沉默領土　剩下燒焦了味道<br />\n現在少點憤怒　多些厚道　偶爾也很躁<br />\n不管這種爭拗有型或老套　未做好的繼續做<br />\n活著必須革命　心高氣傲　哪裡去不到<br />\n<br />\n他雖走得早　他青春不老　灰色的軌跡　磨成血路<br />\n<br />\n＃喔　你我霎眼抗戰一周年　香港怎變　永遠企你這一邊<br />\n　喔　哪怕再去抗戰一周年    去到多遠　我也銘記我起點　不會變<br />\n<br />\nRepeat＃＃"},{"pid":"ca743bfb36db0822ef8444a606169da12c15feee","tid":2023911,"uid":80564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a3675ead9abcc2c120bbf8c2f85d1f6ccee590","tid":2023911,"uid":80564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520c3ae45b491b764fe31bdde44fff150ec94529","tid":2023911,"uid":80564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b89188690283592dbad4232c61f9eaf94d613c